Package: swatia
Title: Reusable Adapter Layer for SWAT+ Parameter Calibration Using ISPSO
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: person("Huidae", "Cho",
    email = "grass4u@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a reusable adapter layer that couples SWAT+ with the
    Isolated-Speciation-Based Particle Swarm Optimization (ISPSO) algorithm for
    parameter calibration. The framework enables simulation-based optimization
    by integrating SWAT+ execution, parameter transformation, and objective
    evaluation within an ISPSO-driven search process. Supports parallel
    evaluation and reproducible optimization workflows.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
